snippet.title: Disintegration Developer Presentation - Future Games Show
snippet.description: Disintegration is set in the future where humanity is struggling to survive and human brains are being transferred into robot bodies! Here are the developers of the game to tell us more. Disintegration is coming to PS4, Xbox One and PC June 16th
